## Compliance

This application complies with all license requirements:
- BSD license: Attribution provided, source code available
- Apache 2.0: Attribution provided, license included
- GPLv3: Not applicable to binaries (only to Termux build system)

No modifications have been made to the OpenSSH or OpenSSL binaries.
